OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777399866
OL,3,CBP's profits more than double as US
OL,4,Cwar in Iran spikes oil prices
OL,6,FBP's profits have more than doubled in
OL,7,Fthe last three months as the Iran war
OL,8,Fcontinues to keep the cost of crude
OL,9,Fhigh.
OL,11,FThe oil firm calculated its profit had
OL,12,Fsurged by over 130% to a better-than-
OL,13,Fexpected $3.2 billion (#2.4 billion)
OL,14,Fin the first quarter of 2026 - up from
OL,15,F$1.54 billion (#1.13 billion) in the
OL,16,Fprevious three months.
OL,18,FIt superseded analysts' predictions
OL,19,Fthat BP would have profits of $2.67
OL,20,Fbillion (#1.97 billion) for the
OL,21,Fquarter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
