OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777399866
OL,3,CBP's profits more than double as US
OL,4,Cwar in Iran spikes oil prices
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"This was another quarter of strong
OL,12,Foperational and financial delivery,
OL,13,Fand we made further progress towards
OL,14,Four 2027 targets," CEO Meg O'Neill
OL,15,Fsaid in a statement on Tuesday.
OL,17,FOil prices have risen rapidly since
OL,18,Fthe US and Israel launched a war in
OL,19,FIran on February 28, causing the
OL,20,FStrait of Hormuz, a critical waterway,
OL,21,Fto be almost entirely closed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
