CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777399866
OL,3,CBP's profits more than double as US
OL,4,Cwar in Iran spikes oil prices
OL,6,FMore than a fifth of the world's oil
OL,7,Fwould typically move through the
OL,8,Fessential waterway, which lies between
OL,9,FIran and the United Arab Emirates.
OL,11,FBrent crude - the global benchmark for
OL,12,Fprices - reached close to $120 (#88)
OL,13,Fdollars a barrel at one stage of the
OL,14,Fwar, and as of Tuesday, sits at $110
OL,15,F(#81) a barrel, its highest since an
OL,16,Fagreed US-Iran ceasefire began on
OL,17,FApril 7.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
