CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777399866
OL,3,CBP's profits more than double as US
OL,4,Cwar in Iran spikes oil prices
OL,6,FThe continued spike has caused fuel
OL,7,Fprices to rocket around the world, and
OL,8,FUK energy bills are set to rise when
OL,9,Fthe price cap is next updated on July
OL,10,F1.
OL,12,FCampaigners have called for a windfall
OL,13,Ftax to be applied to companies like
OL,14,FBP, which they say have profited
OL,15,Fduring the Iran war while households
OL,16,Fstruggle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777399866
OL,3,CBP's profits more than double as US
OL,4,Cwar in Iran spikes oil prices
OL,6,FA windfall tax is a one-off, high-rate
OL,7,Flevy imposed by governments when
OL,8,Fcompanies have exceptionally high
OL,9,Fprofits for an unexpected reason they
OL,10,Fare not responsible for.
OL,12,F"Just as we saw in 2022 following
OL,13,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine, fossil
OL,14,Ffuel giants are quids in when global
OL,15,Finstability drastically inflates fuel
OL,16,Fprices," said Mike Childs, head of
OL,17,Fscience, policy and research at
OL,18,FFriends of the Earth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
