FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777399866
OL,3,CBP's profits more than double as US
OL,4,Cwar in Iran spikes oil prices
OL,6,F"But again, it's ordinary people who
OL,7,Fpay the price when soaring energy
OL,8,Fprices threaten to plunge the UK into
OL,9,Fan even deeper cost of living crisis."
OL,11,FBP's shares rose another 3% in Tuesday
OL,12,Fmorning trading, with the stock now
OL,13,Fhaving climbed more than a third
OL,14,Fhigher in the past six months amid a
OL,15,Fboost from the crude rally.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
