CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777399866
OL,3,CBP's profits more than double as US
OL,4,Cwar in Iran spikes oil prices
OL,6,FO'Neill said teams at BP were "playing
OL,7,Ftheir part" to keep oil, gas and
OL,8,Frefined products flowing during "an
OL,9,Fincredibly challenging time" and
OL,10,Faiming to maintain cost-efficient
OL,11,Foperations.
OL,13,F"We are working with customers and
OL,14,Fgovernments to get fuel where it's
OL,15,Fneeded, helping minimise disruption
OL,16,Fand the impact it can have on people's
OL,17,Flives," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
